casebody.data:
Monday, March 7, 1994

MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

93-2216. Climer v. Clyde Evans Market, Inc.

Allen County, No. 1-93-39. This cause is pending before the court on the filing of a motion for an order directing the Court of Appeals for Allen County to certify its record and as a claimed appeal as of right from said court. It appears from the records of this court that appellant has failed to prosecute this cause with the requisite diligence. Upon consideration thereof,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that this cause be, and hereby is, dismissed sua sponte, effective March 3, 1994.
